[I] Lightweight KMS plane library

[T] Libliftoff eases the use of KMS planes from userspace without standing
[T] in your way. Users create "virtual planes" called layers, set KMS
[T] properties on them, and libliftoff will pick hardware planes for
[T] these layers if possible.

[U] https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/emersion/libliftoff

[A] Libliftoff Authors
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

